title: Gucci Aphrodite Medium Shoulder Bag
description: Gucci medium Aphrodite shoulder bag in brown calfskin leather. Featuring gold-toned hardware, adjustable flat leather shoulder strap and magnetic closure on leather strap with GG logo detailing. This opens to a beige microfiber interior with a zip pocket. Approximate dimensions: 38.5cm(L) x 25cm(H) x 3m(D), 50cm shoulder strap drop with additional 107cm detachable & adjustable strap drop. Accompanied by Gucci dustbag. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
